The paper discusses the use of deep neural network models for sequential decision making problems, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence research (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also applies these models to robotics control problems (cs.RO), as well as a sequential prediction task and dependency-parsing from raw image data (cs.CV, cs.CL). Therefore, these five categories are the most likely to be relevant to this paper.
